<div style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px;">
  <h2 style="color: #1C1512; margin-bottom: 8px;">You signed up with {{provider}}</h2>
  <p style="color: #8A7F78; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5;">
    Hi {{firstName}}, we received a password reset request for your account, but it looks like you signed up using <strong>{{provider}}</strong>.
  </p>
  <p style="color: #8A7F78; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5;">
    To sign in, open ChefPixel and tap <strong>Continue with {{provider}}</strong>.
  </p>
  <p style="color: #8A7F78; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; margin-top: 24px;">
    If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.
  </p>
</div>
